description: Elwood's Dog House is Rhode Island's premier mobile hot spot for delicious gourmet dogs and more!  Scratch-made sauces that will knock your socks off!  Additionally, we offer affordable hot dog cart rentals. Freddie, the owner and operator, is a super friendly fellow who thoroughly loves serving his customers.  While the business was only started in February of 2014, Freddie has been in the business of serving people for over 20 years.  At Elwood's, you WILL be taken care of!
name: Elwood's Dog House
